Merge pull request #50 from baoyongzhang/pr/48

support for both swipe directions

Added next possibility: now you can choose swipe direction. Just use method setSwipeDirection() (possible parameters are: SwipeMenuListView.DIRECTION_RIGHT, SwipeMenuListView.DIRECTION_LEFT) for your SwipeMenuListView instance.
